data.description: Move-in ready 3 BR home less than 3 miles from Hurlburt Field. This single story home has great curb appeal with an extended driveway for RV / boat parking. Upon entering, you'll step into the tiled dining/living space with a new sliding glass door that leads you to a spacious Florida room that has views of the backyard... two of the windows were recently installed as well as new siding! Kitchen is L-shaped with plenty of cabinetry and access to the utility room with additional storage. Fresh paint throughout! On the other end of the home are 3 bedrooms (w/ new carpet), one primary with a private full bathroom with step-in shower. New toilets. Backyard is fenced and spacious!! Home has 1 car garage w/ utility sink and fridge. Gas Water Heater 2021. Roof 2010. New AlumiCon connections + GFCI receptacles in home to meet code.
